<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Economic_democracy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=26" title="Edit section: Further reading">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Further reading</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><i>Economic Democracy</i>, <a href="/wiki/C._H._Douglas" title="C. H. Douglas">C. H. Douglas</a> (1920) <i>new edition</i>: December 1974; Bloomfield Books; <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0904656063" class="internal">ISBN 0904656063</a></li>
<li><i>Economic Democracy: A Grand Strategy for World Peace and Prosperity</i>, <a href="/wiki/J.W._Smith" title="J.W. Smith" class="mw-redirect">J.W. Smith</a>, <a href="http://www.ied.info/" class="external text" title="http://www.ied.info/" rel="nofollow">Institute for Economic Democracy</a>, July 2006, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/1933567023" class="internal">ISBN 1933567023</a></li>
<li><i>After Capitalism</i>, <a href="/wiki/David_Schweickart" title="David Schweickart">David Schweickart</a>, Rowman &amp; Littlefield Publishers, Inc., Oct 2002, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0742513009" class="internal">ISBN 0742513009</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.inclusivedemocracy.org/journal/vol4/vol4_no4_takis_economic_crisis.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.inclusivedemocracy.org/journal/vol4/vol4_no4_takis_economic_crisis.htm" rel="nofollow">"The myths about the economic crisis, the reformist left and economic democracy"</a> by <a href="/wiki/Takis_Fotopoulos" title="Takis Fotopoulos">Takis Fotopoulos</a>, The International Journal of <a href="/wiki/Inclusive_Democracy" title="Inclusive Democracy">Inclusive Democracy</a>, vol 4, no 4, October 2008.</li>
<li><i>The War At Home: The Corporate Offensive from Ronald Reagan to George W. Bush</i>, Jack Rasmus, Kyklos Productions, LLC, 2006, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0977106209" class="internal">ISBN 0977106209</a></li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Great_Transformation" title="The Great Transformation">The Great Transformation</a></i>, Karl Polanyi</li>
<li>"Towards an Inclusive Democracy", <a href="/wiki/Takis_Fotopoulos" title="Takis Fotopoulos">Takis Fotopoulos</a>, London/New York 1997 Googlebooks <a href="http://books.google.gr/books?id=3q-Aa-Nl5qUC&amp;printsec=frontcover&amp;dq=Fotopoulos+Takis&amp;ei=FH-6SL_9B4LgywT1xfyIBg&amp;hl=en&amp;sig=ACfU3U3meVXRoz9z2M2mGGOIDYJRI3FeGQ" class="external autonumber" title="http://books.google.gr/books?id=3q-Aa-Nl5qUC&amp;printsec=frontcover&amp;dq=Fotopoulos+Takis&amp;ei=FH-6SL_9B4LgywT1xfyIBg&amp;hl=en&amp;sig=ACfU3U3meVXRoz9z2M2mGGOIDYJRI3FeGQ" rel="nofollow">[1]</a></li>
